## Definition Of Done
- Behavior matches the requested outcome.
- Public contracts are preserved or intentionally documented.
- Tests were added or updated for changed behavior.
- Validation steps were run, or any gaps are called out explicitly.
- Risks, assumptions, and follow-up work are documented.

